# Based on https://www.toptal.com/developers/gitignore/api/macos,csharp,unity
# Unity-specific corrections for this repo:
# - Do not ignore Unity .meta files; they are source and must be tracked.
# - Do not ignore the root Packages/ directory; Unity manifest/lock files are source.
# - Preserve Blockiverse local generated artifacts, secret files, and one-off script ignores.

### Csharp ###
## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.
##
## Get latest from https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore

